data <- Read10X("./dara")
dim(data)
## [1] 48816  6260
seurat <- CreateSeuratObject(data, min.cells = 313, min.features = 700)
dim(seurat)
## [1] 9423 6260
seurat[["percent.mt"]] <- PercentageFeatureSet(seurat, pattern = "^mt-")

FeatureScatter(seurat, "nFeature_RNA", "percent.mt") + scale_x_log10() +
  geom_hline(yintercept = 2.6, lty=2) + geom_vline(xintercept = 1570, lty=2.5)

The lines there show the thrashholds which i have choosen

seurat <- subset(seurat, subset = nFeature_RNA > 1570 & percent.mt < 2.6)
dim(seurat)
## [1] 9423 5461

I will use an old school normalization sryle, becouse SCTransform() doesnt work properly on my (seems like latest) version of Seurat library. It does not clusterize cells well (This issue is also reported by other users on github)

Normalization and visualization

seurat <- NormalizeData(seurat, normalization.method = "LogNormalize", scale.factor = 10000)
 seurat <- FindVariableFeatures(seurat, selection.method = "vst", nfeatures = 2000)
 seurat <- ScaleData(seurat)
seurat <- RunPCA(seurat)
ElbowPlot(seurat, ndims = 50)

top10_variable_genes <- head(VariableFeatures(seurat), 10)
VariableFeaturePlot(seurat) %>%
  LabelPoints(points = top10_variable_genes, repel = TRUE) +
  scale_y_log10()

seurat <- RunTSNE(seurat, dims=1:20)
DimPlot(seurat, reduction = "tsne") + NoLegend()

seurat <- RunUMAP(seurat, dims=1:20)
DimPlot(seurat, reduction = "umap") + NoLegend()

## Clustering Now we will run clusterization. We will work with umap, because it looks more representative in our cese

seurat <- FindNeighbors(seurat, dims = 1:20)
seurat <- FindClusters(seurat, resolution= 0.2)

I have not included erythrosytes because they are not clearly seen in our plots. That is mostly due to more strict filtering settings. ## Top differentially expressed genes

 allMarkers <- FindAllMarkers(seurat, test.use = "MAST", only.pos = T)
goodMarkers <- allMarkers %>% group_by(cluster) %>% top_n(n = 1, wt = avg_log2FC) %>% pull(gene)
goodMarkers
## [1] "Nts"      "Ambn"     "Mt1"      "tg-DsRed" "Bglap"    "Spp1"     "Ccl21a"  
## [8] "Apoe"
FeaturePlot(seurat, goodMarkers[1:10], cols=c("grey", "red"), reduction="umap")
